Git Ignore easy

1) list files which we want to ignore

$ git status
.idea/xyz.xml
.idea/pqr.iml
Output
.DS_Store

2) Copy the content of step#1 and append it into .gitignore file.

$echo "
.idea/xyz.xml
.idea/pqr.iml
Output
.DS_Store" >> .gitignore

3) Validate
$ git status
.gitignore

likewise we can add directory and all of its sub dir/files which we want to ignore in git status using directoryname/* and I executed this command from src directory.
